content: Good app and responsive developer, but there are a few significant issues. (1) It doesn't show the current "Feels Like" temperature in the large widget. Showing this number in the current-weather widgets, and not just in the app can be quite important. (2) It is not possible to show both hourly and daily forecasts in separate rows in the same large widget, although at least it is possible to show them in separate widgets which is okay. I need to be able to see them together in a widget and without having to tap anything. Compare with the Weather Live app, for example, which does show both in a single widget. (3) In a 1 row widget, it doesn't show the time at which the data was refreshed, or an icon to manually refresh it. Tapping on it just opens up the app. I don't necessarily want to refresh it if it has already been recently updated. Compare with the Weather & Clock Widget app, for example, which does show the update time as well as a refresh-icon in its widgets.
